(surface_periphery_inquiry_table) :inquiry_term: /lookup_entry and target_file/ |unresolved_inquiry|
  + [inquiry_term] is the lookup handle exposed by a surface file
  + [lookup_entry] is the table record with target_file, search phrases, relation reason, query mode, and depth hint
  |unresolved_inquiry| missing pointers, stale paths, unindexed surfaces, unsupported semantic identity, and exhaustive coverage claims
